import { Component, OnInit, Input } from '@angular/core'; import { Observable } from 'rxjs'; import { ContentfulService } from '../contentful.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-items', templateUrl: './items.component.html', styleUrls: ['./items.component.css'] }) export class ItemsComponent implements OnInit { @Input() result$: Observable; constructor(private contentfulService: ContentfulService) { this.result$ = contentfulService.retrieveContent(); } ngOnInit() { } }
